snippet.title: Arcade Game: Piranha (1981 GL(US BIlliards License))
snippet.description:
A Pac-Man clone where you play a role of a piranha being chased by 4 octopuses.

Note: Used invincibility cheat after down to last life in case anyone didn't know.
